QuestData.Title: Counting Argali
QuestData.Description:
One of our key resources is our argali herd. Every loss is felt deeply for the strength of our clan.
A few of the argali have gotten separated and have wandered away from the herd. Our shepherds could use your assistance reclaiming them.
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak with the Aylaag Shepherd and return the lost sheep to the clan.
QuestData.RewardText: Thank you. Our clan deeply appreciates the assistance.

Objectives.Objective: Wandering Argali returned to the herd
